    <section id="faq" class="faq-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">FAQs about Healthy Eating</h2>
            <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1"
                            aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1">
                            What is healthy eating?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="faq1"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Healthy eating involves consuming a balanced diet that provides the necessary nutrients for your
                            body,
                            including carbohydrates, proteins, healthy fats, vitamins, and minerals.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
                            What is the ideal number of calories per day?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Caloric needs vary depending on age, gender, and physical activity. On average, men need around
                            2,500
                            calories, while women need around 2,000 calories per day.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
                            How can I maintain a healthy diet when I’m busy?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq3"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            You can maintain a healthy diet by planning meals ahead, choosing healthy snacks, and packing
                            nutritious
                            meals when working or traveling.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq4">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
                            What are the benefits of eating fruits and vegetables?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq4"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Fruits and vegetables are rich in vitamins, minerals, and fiber, which are essential for
                            digestive health,
                            boosting the immune system, and improving skin health. They are also low in calories and help
                            maintain
                            an ideal weight.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq5">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
                            Are carbohydrates bad for the body?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq5"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Carbohydrates are not bad, but it’s important to choose healthy sources like whole grains, brown
                            rice,
                            and vegetables. Complex carbohydrates provide more stable energy and are better for the body.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq6">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6">
                            What are healthy fats?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq6"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Healthy fats come from natural sources such as avocados, nuts, fatty fish like salmon, and olive
                            oil.
                            These fats are beneficial for heart health, brain function, and help absorb vitamins.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq7">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapse7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse7">
                            How can I choose healthy snacks?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse7" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq7"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Choose snacks that are rich in fiber, protein, and healthy fats, such as nuts, fresh fruits, or
                            low-fat
                            yogurt. Avoid snacks with added sugars or trans fats.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq8">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapse8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse8">
                            Does eating dinner affect my weight?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse8" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq8"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            Eating dinner doesn’t directly affect your weight, but choosing light, balanced meals at night
                            can help
                            control calories and improve sleep quality.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq9">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapse9" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse9">
                            What is a balanced diet?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapse9" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq9"
                        data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            A balanced diet is one that includes all food groups: carbohydrates, proteins, healthy fats,
                            vitamins,
                            and minerals to ensure that your body receives all the nutrients it needs.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
